{"tid":2432328,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"成語動畫廊（連登版）01  刻舟求劍","createTime":"2021-03-04T08:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T06:52:13.000Z","uid":258784,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"10bdaebbdb69ed2905de4cdc6f38f64daf369c66","tid":2432328,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:55:48.000Z","msg":"由於早前有巴打提議我將唇亡齒寒嘅成語故事變做連登版，我見大家反應幾好就決定得閒寫下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，等大家重温下成語故事，等平時唔巧用錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大家睇完連登版記得睇返原文，咁先學到嘢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">刻舟求劍</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n從前有一日，有一位連登會然去動漫節嘅時候，用晒佢食咗半年二手飯儲嘅錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，買咗銀魂嗰把洞爺湖刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jA62OXy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjA62OXy.jpg&h=f579fd85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n走嘅時候就諗住玩下毒撚的浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，行過隔離灣仔碼頭坐船返過去尖沙咀，順便嚮船度拎把洞爺湖出嚟影下中二相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，點知毒撚柒開有條路跣手跌咗把刀落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，要知道毒撚係跟游泳健將巴菲特學游水，Molamola半年積蓄咁就冇晒喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過好在佢都幾醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢即刻諗起刻舟求劍個故事，心諗（我先冇咁蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，畫架船就梗係冇用）於是佢拎咗部電話出嚟影低嚮架船邊個位跌咗把刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，打算一陣上岸俾張相個職員睇，等職員幫佢撈返把刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上到岸個毒撚等一時間揾個職員幫手，仲好有自信咁Show咗張相係個職員睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，個毒撚同個職員講：「我就係嚮呢個位跌咗把刀，我仲影低埋個海，你哋快啲揾人幫我撈返把刀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n個職員講咗句：傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候個毒撚就意識到自己柒L咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢望住個海，再諗返佢呢半年食嘅二手飯&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>原典故：</ins><br />\n<br />\n戰國時，秦國丞相呂不韋在《呂氏春秋》一書中，闡述君王治理國政的道理。他認為君王治國應要符合時宜，不能一味沿襲舊法，因為環境會隨著時間改變。他舉了一個例子：楚國有人渡江時，劍掉到水裡，他便很快地在船身上刻了記號，說：「我的劍就是從這裡掉下去的。」等到船停了，他就從記號處下水找劍。可是船已經走動了，但落水的劍卻不會動，這樣找劍，不是很奇怪嗎？如果用舊法治理國家，而不考慮時空的轉變，就像這個求劍者的行為一樣令人困惑。後來這個典源被濃縮成「刻舟求劍」，用來比喻拘泥固執，不知變通。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>釋義：</ins><br />\n<br />\n劍掉入水中，在船舷刻上記號，待船停止後仍從記號處下水尋劍。比喻拘泥固執，不知變通。<br />\n<br />\n摘自<a href=\"https://pedia.cloud.edu.tw/Entry/Detail?title=%E5%88%BB%E8%88%9F%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%8D&amp;search=%E5%88%BB%E8%88%9F%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%8D&amp;order=keyword_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpedia.cloud.edu.tw%2FEntry%2FDetail%3Ftitle%3D%25E5%2588%25BB%25E8%2588%259F%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%258D%26search%3D%25E5%2588%25BB%25E8%2588%259F%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%258D%26order%3Dkeyword_title&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv6Cfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=e2be3ca0\" target=\"_blank\">https://pedia.cloud.edu.tw/Entry/Detail?title=%E5%88%BB%E8%88%9F%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%8D&amp;search=%E5%88%BB%E8%88%9F%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%8D&amp;order=keyword_title</a>"},{"pid":"3ebf8f37787ae17176b46a2ccbeb7a7217a7d763","tid":2432328,"uid":366401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec2e6205dd01dbeb2e81e7b2bcf6fcecf2b94d2","tid":2432328,"uid":258784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:56:55.000Z","msg":"補返上次唇亡齒寒嘅故事<br />\n<br />\n今日再睇「唇亡齒寒」嘅故事，證明人類總是要犯相同的錯誤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gJeQxT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gJeQxT</a><br />\n#9 回覆 - 分享自 LIHK